STATE
v.
Timothy Lee CREED 35P18-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 1, 2018

Timothy Lee Creed, For Creed, Timothy Lee.

Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of N.C.

Maureen Krueger, District Attorney, for the State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th of January 2018 by Defendant for Leave to File Petition for Writ of Errow, Coram Nobis in Moore County Superior Court:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of March 2018."
